
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "View";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutCarOwner.cshtml";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">




<body>


    <div class="benefit-content">
        <div class="benefits-section">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5 fw-bold ">Have a car for rent? Don't miss out on your benefit</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd "></i>
                            <h5>How the insurance works</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>From the minute you hand the keys over till the second you get them back you are covered. Your private insurance is not affected.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            <h5>It's completely free</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>We offer both owners and renters free sign ups. It's only once a vehicle is rented out that a share is deducted to cover admin and insurance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                            <h5>You decide the price</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>When you list a car you decide the price. We can help with recommendations as to price, but ultimately you decide!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-car"></i>
                            <h5>Handing over your vehicle</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>You arrange the time and location for the exchange of your vehicle with the renter. Both parties will need to agree and sign the vehicle rental sheet before and after key handover.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
                            <h5>You are in charge</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>All renters are pre-screened by us to ensure safety and get your approval. If you do not feel comfortable with someone you are able to decline a booking.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-box">
                        <div class="benefit-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-money-check-alt"></i>
                            <h5>Set payment</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p>We pay you once a month and you can always view how much your car has earned under your user profile.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container benefit-button mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-car">Make money on your car right away</h2>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("AddACar", "Car")'">List Your Car Today</button>
    </div>





    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>

